<body>
  <h1>Huong dan cai dat SQL Server JDBC Driver va cau truc Backend</h1>

  <h2>1. JDBC Driver la gi?</h2>
  <p>
    JDBC Driver la thu vien giup Java ket noi va lam viec voi database. Voi project nay,
    Backend dung SQL Server nen can Microsoft SQL Server JDBC Driver.
  </p>
  <p>
    Neu chi ket noi SQL Server bang username/password thi thuong chi can <code>mssql-jdbc</code>.
    Neu muon dung Windows Authentication, project can them <code>mssql-jdbc_auth</code> de co file DLL native.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Project hien dang dung driver nao?</h2>
  <p>Trong <code>Backend/pom.xml</code>, project da co 2 dependency quan trong:</p>
  <pre>&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;com.microsoft.sqlserver&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;mssql-jdbc&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;scope&gt;runtime&lt;/scope&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;

&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;com.microsoft.sqlserver&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;mssql-jdbc_auth&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;13.2.1.x64&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;type&gt;dll&lt;/type&gt;
  &lt;scope&gt;runtime&lt;/scope&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre>

  <p>Y nghia:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>mssql-jdbc</code>: driver JDBC chinh de Java noi chuyen voi SQL Server.</li>
    <li><code>mssql-jdbc_auth</code>: file DLL ho tro Windows Authentication.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Cach cai dat JDBC Driver bang Maven</h2>
  <p>
    Vi project dung Maven, minh khong can tai file jar thu cong. Chi can chay Maven,
    Maven se tai dependency trong <code>pom.xml</code> ve thu muc local <code>.m2</code>.
  </p>
  <pre>cd Backend
.\mvnw.cmd dependency:resolve</pre>

  <p>Sau khi tai xong:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>mssql-jdbc</code> se nam trong <code>C:\Users\HIEN\.m2\repository\com\microsoft\sqlserver\mssql-jdbc</code>.</li>
    <li><code>mssql-jdbc_auth</code> se nam trong <code>C:\Users\HIEN\.m2\repository\com\microsoft\sqlserver\mssql-jdbc_auth\13.2.1.x64</code>.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>File DLL can cho Windows Authentication:</p>
  <pre>C:\Users\HIEN\.m2\repository\com\microsoft\sqlserver\mssql-jdbc_auth\13.2.1.x64\mssql-jdbc_auth-13.2.1.x64.dll</pre>

  <h2>4. Cau hinh ket noi database hien tai</h2>
  <p>Trong <code>Backend/src/main/resources/application.properties</code>:</p>
  <pre>spring.datasource.url=jdbc:sqlserver://localhost:1433;databaseName=clubmanage;integratedSecurity=true;encrypt=true;trustServerCertificate=true
spring.datasource.driver-class-name=com.microsoft.sqlserver.jdbc.SQLServerDriver</pre>

  <p>Y nghia connection string:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>localhost:1433</code>: ket noi SQL Server tren may hien tai, port 1433.</li>
    <li><code>databaseName=clubmanage</code>: dung database ten <code>clubmanage</code>.</li>
    <li><code>integratedSecurity=true</code>: dung Windows Authentication.</li>
    <li><code>encrypt=true</code> va <code>trustServerCertificate=true</code>: cho phep ket noi co ma hoa va tin certificate local.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Cau hinh de Java tim thay DLL</h2>
  <p>
    Khi dung Windows Authentication, Java phai biet vi tri file DLL.
    Project da cau hinh san trong <code>pom.xml</code>:
  </p>
  <pre>-Djava.library.path=${user.home}/.m2/repository/com/microsoft/sqlserver/mssql-jdbc_auth/13.2.1.x64</pre>

  <p>Chay app bang Maven:</p>
  <pre>cd Backend
.\mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run</pre>

  <p>Neu chay bang IntelliJ IDEA, them VM options:</p>
  <pre>-Djava.library.path=C:\Users\HIEN\.m2\repository\com\microsoft\sqlserver\mssql-jdbc_auth\13.2.1.x64</pre>

  <h2>6. SQL Server can chuan bi gi?</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>SQL Server phai dang chay.</li>
    <li>TCP/IP nen duoc bat va port 1433 phai dung voi connection string.</li>
    <li>Database <code>clubmanage</code> phai ton tai.</li>
    <li>Windows user dang chay app phai co quyen login vao SQL Server.</li>
    <li>User do can co quyen tren database <code>clubmanage</code>.</li>
  </ol>

  <p>Neu dung SQL Server Express instance, connection string co the can doi thanh:</p>
  <pre>spring.datasource.url=jdbc:sqlserver://localhost\\SQLEXPRESS;databaseName=clubmanage;integratedSecurity=true;encrypt=true;trustServerCertificate=true</pre>

  <h2>7. Loi thuong gap</h2>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>Loi</th>
      <th>Nguyen nhan</th>
      <th>Cach xu ly</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>no mssql-jdbc_auth in java.library.path</code></td>
      <td>Java khong tim thay file DLL.</td>
      <td>Them <code>-Djava.library.path</code> vao VM options hoac chay bang <code>.\mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run</code>.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>Login failed for user</code></td>
      <td>Windows user hien tai chua co quyen trong SQL Server.</td>
      <td>Them Windows user vao SQL Server Login va cap quyen cho database <code>clubmanage</code>.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>Cannot connect to localhost:1433</code></td>
      <td>SQL Server chua chay, chua bat TCP/IP, sai port, hoac dung sai instance.</td>
      <td>Kiem tra SQL Server Configuration Manager va connection string.</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h2>8. So luoc chuc nang cac folder trong Backend</h2>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>Folder/File</th>
      <th>Chuc nang</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>Backend/.mvn</code></td>
      <td>Cau hinh Maven Wrapper, giup chay Maven bang <code>mvnw.cmd</code> ma khong can cai Maven global.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>Backend/src</code></td>
      <td>Chua source code chinh cua ung dung.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>src/main/java</code></td>
      <td>Chua code Java cua Spring Boot backend.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>com/example/demo/DemoApplication.java</code></td>
      <td>File main de khoi dong ung dung Spring Boot.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>config</code></td>
      <td>Chua cau hinh he thong nhu async executor va seed data mau.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>controller</code></td>
      <td>Chua REST API endpoint. Moi folder con thuong dai dien cho mot nhom chuc nang nhu department, member, event, finance.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>application</code></td>
      <td>Tang xu ly use-case cua app, gom DTO, mapper, service va exception.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>application/dto</code></td>
      <td>Chua object request/response, dung de nhan du lieu tu client va tra du lieu ve client.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>application/mapper</code></td>
      <td>Chuyen doi giua Entity va DTO.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>application/service</code></td>
      <td>Chua logic nghiep vu o tang ung dung, controller thuong goi vao service nay.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>domain</code></td>
      <td>Tang domain/database cua he thong.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>domain/model</code></td>
      <td>Chua Entity JPA, moi class thuong anh xa voi bang trong database.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>domain/repository</code></td>
      <td>Chua Spring Data JPA repository de truy van database.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>domain/service</code></td>
      <td>Chua logic domain gan voi nghiep vu cot loi.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>domain/enums</code></td>
      <td>Chua cac enum nhu trang thai, loai giao dich, gioi tinh, trang thai duyet.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>src/main/resources</code></td>
      <td>Chua file cau hinh runtime, quan trong nhat la <code>application.properties</code>.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>Backend/data</code></td>
      <td>Dang co file database H2 local cu hoac test local.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>Backend/target</code></td>
      <td>Folder build output do Maven tao ra, khong can sua tay.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>Backend/pom.xml</code></td>
      <td>File cau hinh Maven: dependency, plugin, Java version va cau hinh build.</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h2>9. Seed data nam o dau?</h2>
  <p>
    Seed data nam trong file:
    <code>Backend/src/main/java/com/example/demo/config/SampleDataSeeder.java</code>.
  </p>
  <p>
    Class <code>SampleDataSeeder</code> implement <code>CommandLineRunner</code>, nen Spring Boot se tu dong goi method
    <code>run()</code> khi ung dung khoi dong.
  </p>
  <p>
    Trong <code>run()</code>, code kiem tra neu da co du lieu trong cac bang chinh nhu role, department, subject,
    document type hoac member thi se khong seed nua.
  </p>

  <h3>Cac nhom seed hien co</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><code>seedRoles()</code>: tao role mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedDepartments()</code>: tao department mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedSubjects()</code>: tao mon hoc mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedDocumentTypes()</code>: tao loai tai lieu mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedMembers()</code>: tao thanh vien mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedUsers()</code>: tao user dang nhap mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedEventRoles()</code>, <code>seedEvents()</code>, <code>seedEventOrganizers()</code>: tao du lieu event.</li>
    <li><code>seedDocuments()</code>, <code>seedDocumentFiles()</code>: tao tai lieu va file mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedNotifications()</code>, <code>seedNotificationRecipients()</code>: tao thong bao mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedTransactions()</code>: tao giao dich tai chinh mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedSystemSettings()</code>: tao cau hinh he thong mau.</li>
    <li><code>seedAuditLogs()</code>: tao audit log mau.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>10. Tom tat nhanh</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Muon Java ket noi SQL Server: can <code>mssql-jdbc</code>.</li>
    <li>Muon Java dung Windows Authentication: can them <code>mssql-jdbc_auth</code> va file DLL.</li>
    <li>Project da khai bao ca hai trong <code>pom.xml</code>.</li>
    <li>Chay <code>.\mvnw.cmd dependency:resolve</code> de tai driver ve may.</li>
    <li>Seed data nam trong <code>SampleDataSeeder.java</code>.</li>
  </ul>
</body>
</html>
